<section class="about-mission">
  <div class="about-mission-image">
    <img src="/images/left.jpg" alt="BridgeDegree – career infrastructure for Nigerian students">
  </div>
  <div class="about-mission-content">
      <h2>Our story</h2>
      <p class="about-mission-lead">BridgeDegree is Nigeria's Embedded Career Infrastructure Layer, built by Nigerians, for Nigerians, who have lived the painful gap between earning a degree and gaining real global leverage.</p>
      <p>We were founded on a clear, hard-earned truth: Nigeria produces extraordinary talent every year, sharp, capable, determined, yet the world consistently underestimates or overlooks our graduates. Not because of lack of ability, intelligence, or potential, but because of missing documentation, positioning, and structured access to global opportunities.</p>
      <p>Most platforms try to address this after graduation through courses, bootcamps, or short placements. BridgeDegree takes a fundamentally different approach. We are an operating system that sits between the Nigerian university and the global economy, embedded directly into the university journey from 100 Level through graduation, NYSC, and beyond.</p>
      <p class="about-quote">Our mission is straightforward and uncompromising: By the time a BridgeDegree student collects their certificate and walks across that graduation stage, they are already positioned, published, and proven, carrying 2+ years of verifiable work experience, at least one co-authored indexed publication, blockchain-verified credentials in a tamper-proof Career Passport, and a clear, personalized pathway to a successful life.</p>
      <p>We don't wait for the system to change. We build the infrastructure layer that makes the change inevitable.</p>
  </div>
</section>

