  <div class="container">
    <h2>Why we exist</h2>
    <p>Nigeria produces over 600,000 graduates every year. Most are qualified. Nearly all are invisible to employers, not because they lack ability, but because the university system produces academic records and nothing else. No verified work history. No published research. No globally legible career profile.</p>
    <p>BridgeDegree was founded in 2026 to solve this at the structural level. We give students a way to build proof while they study, so that by graduation, they hold credentials any employer, anywhere, can verify in seconds.</p>
  </div>
</section>

