      <li><strong>Earned access</strong> — BridgeDegree is not an open programme. Graduates earn their Career Passports through years of structured work, research, and professional development.</li>
      <li><strong>Nigerian talent, global standards</strong> — We hold our graduates to the same standard as the best talent development programmes worldwide. Nigerian graduates deserve nothing less.</li>
